==== 当前代码 ====
```cryptol
module BitsToBytes where

// Converts a bit array of length multiple of 8 into a byte array.
// Each byte is formed as: B[j] = sum_{i=0}^{7} b[8*j + i] * 2^i
BitsToBytes : {n} (fin n, n % 8 == 0) => [n] -> [n/8][8]
BitsToBytes b = [ byteAt j | j <- [0 .. (n/8 - 1)] ]
  where
    byteAt : [32] -> [8]
    byteAt j = sum [ bitToInt (b @ (8*j + i)) * (1 << i) | i <- [0 .. 7] ]

    bitToInt : Bit -> [8]
    bitToInt x = if x then 1 else 0
```

